OL,3,CInjunction preventing bin workers from
OL,4,Cblocking lorries granted indefinitely
OL,6,FAn injunction brought by Birmingham
OL,7,FCity Council to stop striking bin
OL,8,Fworkers from obstructing bin lorries
OL,9,Fhas been extended indefinitely.
OL,11,FThe council said the injunction aims
OL,12,Fto ensure bin lorries can leave to
OL,13,Fclear the thousands of tonnes of
OL,14,Frubbish that has built up during the
OL,15,Findustrial action.
OL,17,FIt said Unite the Union had already
OL,18,Fagreed to a consent order for the
OL,19,Finjunction to be extended, which has
OL,20,Fnow been ratified by the High Court.
