OL,6,FA meeting was due to take place today
OL,7,Fwhere the injunction was going to be
OL,8,Fdiscussed, but that was cancelled.
OL,10,FBirmingham City Council said: "We are
OL,11,Fpleased that the court has ratified
OL,12,Fthe Consent Order agreed with Unite
OL,13,Fyesterday that the injunction, which
OL,14,Fwas granted by the High Court on
OL,15,FFriday 23 May, will continue on an
OL,16,Findefinite basis.
