OL,6,F"This means that there will not be a
OL,7,Fcourt hearing at 2pm today. This
OL,8,Fshould ensure that vehicles are freely
OL,9,Fable to leave their depots and that
OL,10,Fworkers are also able to continue to
OL,11,Fcollect waste from the city.
OL,13,F"We have also agreed with Unite that
OL,14,Fthe legal costs which the council
OL,15,Fincurred in securing the original
OL,16,Finjunction will be dealt with by the
OL,17,Fcourt at a later date.
