OL,3,CInjunction preventing bin workers from
OL,4,Cblocking lorries granted indefinitely
OL,6,FMembers of Unite have been on all-out
OL,7,Fstrike since March 11th in a row over
OL,8,Fpay and jobs, leading to bags of
OL,9,Frefuse piling up across the city.
OL,11,FThe injunction had been granted last
OL,12,Fweek, which the council said allowed
OL,13,Ftheir trucks out of all of their
OL,14,Fdepots on Monday morning (May 26th).
OL,16,FA Unite the Union spokesperson said:
OL,17,F"Unite has agreed to abide by the law
OL,18,Fon picketing and we will continue to
OL,19,Fconduct a lawful, peaceful picket.
