OL,6,F"Whilst the injunction will remain in
OL,7,Fplace, both parties are entitled to
OL,8,Fapply to the court at any time in
OL,9,Frelation to the order. Birmingham City
OL,10,FCouncil is fully aware of this.
OL,12,F"The union is preparing evidence to be
OL,13,Fable to seek to persuade the court
OL,14,Fthat the interim injunction should not
OL,15,Fhave been granted last Friday evening.
